{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"1857e059-de5d-4bcb-8b0d-0436b5429403","content":"No files found in the working directory. Since there's no existing file, here's exactly what you need to do:\n\n## Converting to Compiled Bindings\n\nAdd `x:DataType` to your `ContentPage` root element, pointing at your ViewModel:\n\n```xml\n<ContentPage xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n             xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n             xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"\n             x:Class=\"YourApp.Views.SettingsPage\"\n             x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\">\n\n    <VerticalStackLayout Padding=\"20\" Spacing=\"15\">\n\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding Theme}\" />\n\n        <Switch IsToggled=\"{Binding NotificationsEnabled}\" />\n\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding FontSize, StringFormat='Font size: {0}'}\" />\n        <Stepper Value=\"{Binding FontSize}\" Minimum=\"8\" Maximum=\"32\" />\n\n    </VerticalStackLayout>\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\n**Key change:** the `x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"` attribute tells the XAML compiler to resolve all `{Binding ...}` expressions against `SettingsViewModel` at compile time.\n\n## Catching Binding Errors at Build Time\n\n**1. Enable strict mode** — add this to your `.csproj`:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <!-- Treat invalid compiled bindings as build errors -->\n  <MauiStrictXamlCompilation>true</MauiStrictXamlCompilation>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n**2. What this catches:** If you typo a property (e.g., `{Binding Themee}`), or bind to a wrong type, the build will **fail** instead of silently producing a runtime null.\n\n**3. Opt out locally** when needed (e.g., for a dynamically-typed section):\n\n```xml\n<CollectionView x:DataType=\"{x:Null}\" ItemsSource=\"{Binding DynamicItems}\" />\n```\n\nSetting `x:DataType=\"{x:Null}\"` disables compiled bindings for that element's subtree, falling back to reflection-based binding.\n\n## Summary\n\n| What | How |\n|---|---|\n| Enable compiled bindings | `x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"` on the page |\n| Build-time error on typos | `<MauiStrictXamlCompilation>true</MauiStrictXamlCompilation>` in `.csproj` |\n| Opt out for dynamic data | `x:DataType=\"{x:Null}\"` on specific elements |","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"11bfdbf0-8e99-454b-9c09-85582639fa01","outputTokens":653,"requestId":"B7D1:3A1214:11A9B8:174A80:69FFD736"},"id":"fea6953e-6e43-470d-b158-59a966284f49","timestamp":"2026-05-10T00:54:27.063Z","parentId":"6a3b5fdb-5c62-4d0e-87c1-e44af8693488"}
